  <h2>The Colorado Springs Local Market</h2>

  <p>Colorado Springs is one of the fastest-growing mid-sized cities in the country — and that growth is a direct tailwind for a new landscaping business. More new homes means more first-time landscaping clients. More established homeowners means more recurring maintenance demand.</p>

